{"tid":979751,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚試咗盒18禁咖喱，辣到頂唔順","createTime":"2019-01-13T03:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T10:27:59.000Z","uid":75232,"like":642,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"029dd20d9c8677e96ca9dbae2e46b422e6cc8de5","tid":979751,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早排買咗盒日本出嘅18禁咖喱，尋晚見老婆唔喺屋企就叮嚟食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPndtg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPndtg7.jpg&h=77342bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食頭幾啖以為佢無料到，點之原來佢啲後勁好勁。好彩屋企有奶(但係我有乳糖不耐症) 。結果我食咗半盒飯，飲咗成公升奶之後頂唔順放棄咗。<br />\n<br />\n再過咗陣，我啲乳糖不耐症開始嚟料。就係咁，我尋晚搵咗自己笨柒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70aa88bed4db76eec70f7b0912f5ed6bb8110789","tid":979751,"uid":33359,"like":189,"dislike":0,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"渣GA"},{"pid":"445b557949ba8e1b2b2f202035f803f81a1bae75","tid":979751,"uid":55851,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"惺咁渣ga"},{"pid":"ec628d476711dad483360e3e4e0e0721e1baf6ef","tid":979751,"uid":37458,"like":330,"dislike":13,"score":317,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"個兜似比狗食"},{"pid":"3d078f9dc4480ab0e3f751c8cfaee87b4a2d452f","tid":979751,"uid":75232,"like":249,"dislike":6,"score":243,"quote":{"pid":"ec628d476711dad483360e3e4e0e0721e1baf6ef","tid":979751,"uid":37458,"like":330,"dislike":13,"score":317,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"個兜似比狗食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"返工帶飯係用呢隻Pyrex玻璃兜啫...一支公求求其其叮熱佢咪算囉。使唔使用隻好靚嘅碟裝丫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a08ce0c7fded6161654af89645239e3eb740cb","tid":979751,"uid":75232,"like":13,"dislike":34,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"70aa88bed4db76eec70f7b0912f5ed6bb8110789","tid":979751,"uid":33359,"like":189,"dislike":0,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T